snippet.title: Tennis World Tour 2 | New-Gen Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Who's ready for the ultimate Tennis World Tour 2 experience? Featuring a star-packed roster, the addition of the ATP Cup, unique player profiles, and more, The Tennis World Tour 2 has never been more complete.

Tennis World Tour 2 is available now on Xbox Series X|S and PlayStation 5. Owners of the Ace Edition of Tennis World Tour 2 or people who've purchased the Annual Pass are eligible for an upgrade to the Complete Edition.
